   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Hey Guys, Thanks for the prompt response. Following @brittag's suggestion, I
checked a few blog posts that used the same &lt;h3&gt; tags that could do with a
boldening of the title. So I located the common &lt;h3&gt; that could affect all these
posts at "mysite/static/css/blog-style.css". I added an extra "font-weight:
bold" at line 221. I have submitted a merge request on Github as per the
guidelines. Could you please take a look and review the change. 

My earlier comment about blog-style.css not being the correct file was incorrect
(Sincere apologies!)

P.S. This is my first time contributing to an open source project. Thx for all
the help. :)</pre>
