   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Within blog posts (like <a href="http://openhatch.org/blog/2014/newsletter-january-2014/">http://openhatch.org/blog/2014/newsletter-january-2014/</a> for example), 
the headers (&lt;h3&gt;s like "New projects in the OpenHatch volunteer opportunity finder") are not very 
distinguished from the text. It'd be helpful for headers to be slightly bold.

Susan pointed this out, and I agreed!</pre>
   </td>
